### Initialize TanStack Query with static initial data and staleTime (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/tanstack/query/blob/main/docs/framework/angular/guides/initial-query-data.md

This `injectQuery` configuration displays `initialTodos` immediately. The `staleTime: 1000` option prevents refetching for 1 second, meaning new data will only be fetched after an interaction event occurs and 1 second has passed since the query was last considered fresh.

```ts
result = injectQuery(() => ({
  queryKey: ['todos'],
  queryFn: () => fetch('/todos'),
  initialData: initialTodos,
  staleTime: 1000,
}))
```

