### Ensure Query Data - TanStack Query

Source: https://github.com/tanstack/query/blob/main/docs/reference/QueryClient.md

Asynchronously retrieve cached query data or fetch it if unavailable. Returns Promise<TData> with the query results. Supports optional revalidateIfStale parameter to refetch stale data in the background while returning cached data immediately.

```typescript
const data = await queryClient.ensureQueryData({ queryKey, queryFn })
```

