### Invalidate Queries with TanStack Query Client

Source: https://github.com/tanstack/query/blob/main/docs/reference/QueryClient.md

Invalidates and refetches single or multiple queries in the cache based on query keys or other properties. It can control whether active or inactive queries refetch and whether to refetch none, all, or specific types. Options include `throwOnError` and `cancelRefetch`.

```tsx
await queryClient.invalidateQueries(
  {
    queryKey: ['posts'],
    exact,
    refetchType: 'active',
  },
  { throwOnError, cancelRefetch },
)
```

