### Prefetch Infinite Query - TanStack Query

Source: https://github.com/tanstack/query/blob/main/docs/reference/QueryClient.md

Asynchronously prefetch and cache an infinite query before it is needed. Similar to prefetchQuery but designed for infinite queries. Returns a Promise<void> that resolves after execution or immediately if no fetch is needed.

```typescript
await queryClient.prefetchInfiniteQuery({ queryKey, queryFn })
```

